name: Concepticon
body:
### Concepticon

* If you want to browse our concept list, just use the [CSV-Browser](browse.html).
* If you want to compare your own concept list with our concepticon, just use the [CSV-Merger](merge.html).
* If you want to compare two or more of the concept lists in our database, just use our [Comparison-Tool](compare.html).
